irst outings\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CAP-HAITIEN - Four athletes have competed for Haiti so far at the Olympic Games Paris 2024, swimmer Alexandre Grand'Pierre, gymnast Lynnzee Brown, judoka Philippe Metellus and boxer Cedrick Belony-Duli\\u00e8pre.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cap-Ha\\u00eftien\", \"score\": 0.9989266731990675, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CAP-HAITIEN\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cap-Ha\\u00eftien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cap-Ha\\u00eftien\"}, {\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9999997685017928, \"rank\": 2.31450721953284e-07, \"text\": \"Haiti\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmer Alexandre Grand'Pierre\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnast Lynnzee Brown\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"judoka Philippe Metellus\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"boxer Cedrick Belony-Duli\\u00e8pre\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they won the hearts of scores of Haitians worldwide, all of them were however eliminated in the first round.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9551067323010364, \"rank\": 0.04700142227962617, \"text\": \"Haitians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hearts\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"scores\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grand'Pierre was the first athlete to represent Haiti in swimming, competing in the 100-meter breaststroke on July 27.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9999997685017928, \"rank\": 2.31450721953284e-07, \"text\": \"Haiti\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Grand'Pierre\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the first athlete\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter breaststroke\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grand'Pierre swam the race in 1:02.85, finishing fourth in his heat and in 28th position overall out of 35 participants.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Grand'Pierre\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"1:02.85\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"his heat\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"28th position\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"35 participants\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the first 16 swimmers qualified for the semi-finals, hence Grand'Pierre was eliminated.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only the first 16 swimmers\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand'Pierre\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for our free newsletters.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our free newsletters\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 21 years